                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "span",
                      "value": "Viec dieu chinh chi dao hinh anh gan day da cho thay su tien bo khich le voi cac mo hinh da phuong tien lon nguon mo (LMM) nhu LLaVA va MiniGPT-4. Tuy nhien, hau het cac nghien cuu ve LMM nguon mo duoc thuc hien voi cac mo hinh co 13B tham so hoac nho hon. Trong bai bao nay, chung toi trinh bay mot nghien cuu thuc nghiem ve viec mo rong LLaVA len toi 33B va 65B/70B, va chia se nhung phat hien tu cac kham pha cua chung toi ve do phan giai hinh anh, tron du lieu va cac phuong phap dao tao tiet kiem tham so nhu LoRA/QLoRA. Nhung nay duoc danh gia dua tren anh huong cua chung doi voi kha nang da phuong tien va ngon ngu khi hoan thanh cac nhiem vu thuc te trong moi truong hoang da. Chung toi tim thay viec mo rong LMM lien tuc cai thien hieu suat mo hinh va cai thien kha nang ngon ngu, va hieu suat cua viec dieu chinh LoRA/QLoRA cua LMM tuong duong voi hieu suat cua viec tinh chinh toan bo mo hinh. Ngoai ra, nghien cuu nay noi bat tam quan trong cua viec tang do phan giai hinh anh va tron du lieu da phuong tien-ngon ngu de cai thien hieu suat LMM, va dieu chinh chi dao hinh anh doi khi co the cai thien kha nang ngon ngu nguyen ban cua LMM. Chung toi hy vong rang nghien cuu nay lam cho nghien cuu LMM tien tien hon tai quy mo lon hon tro nen de tiep can hon, do do giup xay dung cac co so du lieu manh me hon cho cac nghien cuu tuong lai. Ma nguon va cac diem kiem tra se duoc cong khai."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
